                <div class="Item-BodyWrap">
            <div class="Item-Body">
                <div class="Message">
                    I have successfully connected my Bluetooth speakers to my UM7300 TV, but once I turn off the TV and then turn it back on, it will not auto connect to the speakers.&nbsp; I have to manually connect every time.&nbsp; This is a procedure I am not happy with.&nbsp; Is there something I am not doing right?                </div>
