                <div class="Item-BodyWrap">
                    <div class="Item-Body">
                        <div class="Message">
                            <p>Do the speakers turn on when the TV is powered on? If so,&nbsp;do an A/V reset on the TV. You would do this by pressing the MUTE button 3 times on the LG remote and selecting A/V reset in the menu. This would reset the sound and picture settings back to the factory default. </p><p>If they do not turn on, this would need to be addressed on the speaker's end. </p>                        </div>
